        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">
          Frequently Asked Questions
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-white mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto drop-shadow-md">
          Everything you need to know about selling your kids' items at Kid to Kid Garner
        </p>
