          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 12: Can you send me a digital payout? -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border-l-4 border-warm-orange p-8 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-k2k-blue mb-4">Can you send me a digital payout?</h3>
          <div class="text-charcoal text-lg space-y-3">
            <p>Yes, we can! Your digital payout will be the same amount as cash.</p>
            <p>We will send you a link that will let you choose a variety of digital payout options, including virtual gift cards, Venmo and Paypal.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
